---
// Features section — Brutalist bento-box grid with shared 2px borders
---

<section id="features" class="features-band" aria-labelledby="features-headline">
  <div class="page-container">
    <div class="features-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">WHY MP4YT</span>
      <h2 id="features-headline" class="display-lg features-title">
        BUILT DIFFERENT.<br/>BUILT BETTER.
      </h2>
      <p class="body-md features-subtitle">
        No mirrors, no muxing delays, no file servers. Just a clean serverless pipeline
        that fetches the direct CDN URL and hands it straight to your browser.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bento-box grid -->
    <div class="features-bento">
      <!-- Feature 1: Zero Storage -->
      <article class="bento-cell" aria-labelledby="feat-1-title">
        <h3 id="feat-1-title" class="display-md feat-title">ZERO DISK STORAGE</h3>
        <p class="body-md feat-desc">
          We never save your video on any server. The backend acts as a pure metadata proxy —
          it reads the CDN stream URL and immediately passes it to your browser.
          Your data stays yours.
        </p>
        <div class="feat-tags">
          <span class="feat-tag">MEMORY_SAFE</span>
          <span class="feat-tag">NO_LOGS</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 2: Instant CDN -->
      <article class="bento-cell" aria-labelledby="feat-2-title">
        <h3 id="feat-2-title" class="display-md feat-title">DIRECT CDN STREAM</h3>
        <p class="body-md feat-desc">
          Get the actual streaming URL from the platform's CDN — the same link the platform
          uses to serve the video to you. No re-encoding, no extra hops, maximum speed.
        </p>
        <div class="feat-tags">
          <span class="feat-tag">FAST_PATH</span>
          <span class="feat-tag">COBALT_V4</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 3: 1000+ Platforms -->
      <article class="bento-cell" aria-labelledby="feat-3-title">
        <h3 id="feat-3-title" class="display-md feat-title">1000+ PLATFORMS</h3>
        <p class="body-md feat-desc">
          Powered by Cobalt, the world's most comprehensive media downloader engine.
          Instagram, TikTok, Twitter/X, Reddit, Vimeo, Twitch — paste any URL.
        </p>
        <div class="feat-tags">
          <span class="feat-tag">UNIVERSAL</span>
          <span class="feat-tag">RAW_DATA</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 4: Auto-paste -->
      <article class="bento-cell" aria-labelledby="feat-4-title">
        <h3 id="feat-4-title" class="display-md feat-title">SMART AUTO-PASTE</h3>
        <p class="body-md feat-desc">
          Copy a video URL anywhere on your device and press <kbd class="kbd-inline">Ctrl+V</kbd>
          anywhere on our page. We detect the clipboard content and begin extraction automatically
          — no need to click the input field.
        </p>
        <div class="feat-tags">
          <span class="feat-tag">UX_MACRO</span>
          <span class="feat-tag">HEURISTIC</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 5: Smart Link Sharing -->
      <article class="bento-cell" aria-labelledby="feat-5-title">
        <h3 id="feat-5-title" class="display-md feat-title">SMART LINK SHARING</h3>
        <p class="body-md feat-desc">
          Share a <code class="code-inline">/watch?url=</code> link anywhere. Bots get a beautifully
          rendered OpenGraph preview with the real video title and thumbnail. Humans get
          instantly redirected to the app with the URL pre-filled.
        </p>
        <div class="feat-tags">
          <span class="feat-tag">EDGE_SEO</span>
          <span class="feat-tag">OPENGRAPH</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Feature 6: No Registration -->
      <article class="bento-cell" aria-labelledby="feat-6-title">
        <h3 id="feat-6-title" class="display-md feat-title">NO ACCOUNT NEEDED</h3>
        <p class="body-md feat-desc">
          No sign-up, no email, no OAuth, no cookies tracking you across sessions.
          Open the page, paste a URL, download the video. That's the entire product.
        </p>
        <div class="feat-tags">
          <span class="feat-tag">OPEN</span>
          <span class="feat-tag">FREE</span>
          <span class="feat-tag">INSTANT</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-band {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
    padding: var(--sp-5xl) var(--sp-lg);
  }

  .features-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: var(--sp-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3xl);
  }

  .features-title {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .features-subtitle {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
    color: var(--color-body);
  }

  /* Bento-box grid: shared 2px borders */
  .features-bento {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    border: var(--border);
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .bento-cell {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-md);
    padding: var(--sp-lg);
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
    transition: background-color 0.1s ease;
  }

  .bento-cell:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
  }

  .feat-title {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .feat-desc {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-body);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .feat-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-xs);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: var(--sp-md);
  }

  .feat-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: var(--border);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    background: transparent;
  }

  .kbd-inline {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    border: var(--border);
    padding: 0 5px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .code-inline {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    border: var(--border-thin);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-bento { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .features-band { padding: var(--sp-4xl) var(--sp-md); }
    .features-header { margin-bottom: var(--sp-xl); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .features-band { padding: var(--sp-3xl) var(--sp-sm); }
    .bento-cell { padding: var(--sp-md); }
    .feat-desc { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; }
  }
</style>
